  <brief_title>An Observational Study on The Correlation Between Time of Initiation of Avastin (Bevacizumab) Treatment And Progression-Free Survival in Patients With Colorectal Cancer (CRONOS 1)</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Correlation Between the Moment of Bevacizumab theRapy initiatiOn and the Efficacy in patieNt With cOlorectal Cancer Treated With AvaStin Based First Line Regimens (CRONOS 1)</official_title>
