    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adult patients, &gt;/= the 18 years of age

          -  Previously untreated metastatic colorectal cancer

          -  Scheduled to start 1st line chemotherapeutic treatment

          -  ECOG performance status 0-1

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any conditions included in contraindication list for Avastin

          -  Prior chemotherapy for metastatic colorectal cancer

          -  Adjuvant/neoadjuvant chemotherapy or radio-chemotherapy of non-metastatic colorectal
             cancer completed &lt;6 months prior to treatment start
      </textblock>
